{"tid":2142029,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"測違指引 卓健教市民通街留唾液","createTime":"2020-08-06T06:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T11:16:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b04e37643e9fd544e016744655b1d7e2ca75cfb","tid":2142029,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/7UHKGU74F44HHF2UTXD3E72ASU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2F7UHKGU74F44HHF2UTXD3E72ASU%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOtlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=bdedfddf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2F7UHKGU74F44HHF2UTXD3E72ASU%2F&h=9463dcb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/7UHKGU74F44HHF2UTXD3E72ASU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n測違指引 卓健教市民通街留唾液<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】私家診所提供武漢肺炎病毒檢測出現漏洞，繼近日盈健醫療集團調景嶺港鐵站醫療中心的樣本收集箱滿瀉，不少樣本散落一地後，卓健醫療亦被踢爆有職員教客人在公眾地方或廁所留樣本，即時交回診所，恐散播病毒。卓健稱，已發出內部通告提醒職員要跟隨衞生防護中心指引。<br />\n<br />\n有卓健前線員工踢爆，早前有客戶服務部接聽電話的職員，主動教客人於診所登記取樣本樽後，可在空曠地方或廁所留樣本即時交回診所。有診所員工曾向高層反映此做法不妥，若病人已染疫，在公眾地方或廁所留唾液樣本會危及公眾，但意見不獲正視。前線診所職員慨嘆，之前拒絕登記人士即時交回樣本瓶，但客人不滿電話中職員教另一套，往往引起爭拗。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者昨早前往旺角惠豐中心8樓的。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/awQJ9g3OsdX6AzFHS8XdP3cZ0T8=/974x674/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IJESHHHYWYUN2KTG6VFKBWFLSE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FawQJ9g3OsdX6AzFHS8XdP3cZ0T8%3D%2F974x674%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIJESHHHYWYUN2KTG6VFKBWFLSE.gif&h=08349dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德福花園卓健門外，昨早有市民排隊輪候檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指引訂明需家中進行<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：400呎住15人 床貼床衞生差<br />\n<br />\n卓健醫療回應稱，公司得知初期有部份採集樣本的程序並非依據衞生防護中心《收集深喉唾液樣本病人須知》所載程序於。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，九龍灣德福花園的卓健門外，昨。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d203023086263c167a30cf5b7ce8a29f1d062e5f","tid":2142029,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"黃小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c321d2a17654709b3e3e144f656acf82357d4136","tid":2142029,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d203023086263c167a30cf5b7ce8a29f1d062e5f","tid":2142029,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"黃小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"有啲似黃子悅"},{"pid":"a48e6dde9dbd9f26218abd23bb9d2dbba1a6d6ef","tid":2142029,"uid":276676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"gfable<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Dvt-GCvXiZuop0mQ6hGIEuaGTEI=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZPQNCJ3NER7VPWHAUMFJU64PEI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDvt-GCvXiZuop0mQ6hGIEuaGTEI%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZPQNCJ3NER7VPWHAUMFJU64PEI.jpg&h=b3280dc0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}